## ðŸ›  Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React (with React Router, Redux/Context if included)  
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express  
- **Database**: MongoDB / MongoDB Atlas  
- **Authentication**: JWT & Google OAuth  
- **Other Services**: Gmail (for notifications), Razorpay (for payments), Cloudinary (for image storage)


